                            <comment id="263872" author="bzzz" created="Sun, 23 Feb 2020 11:56:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;please try with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12988&quot; title=&quot;improve mount time on huge ldiskfs filesystem&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12988&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12988&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ldiskfs: skip non-loaded groups at cr=0/1 and &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/37626/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/37626/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
